Empress Dragun 🐉 Queen of Social Media. powerful asian women are typically defined as the villain or a weird type of fetish. with this cover i wanted to embody the power of my own truth being a poc female without interpretation. taking away the stereotype. i’m proud to be ASIAN. more than that i’m proud to look asian. my reign as the mother of draguns has just begun... what scares people about my femininity is that i cary it like a man. it takes a lot of balls be a powerful woman... i should know ;) thank u @kingkongmagazine for the cover and my amazing haus of dragun team!
